name.value: Replicate Cobrainer Job Families or Clusters into SAP SuccessFactors

wrapContent.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<EMEvent>
    <EMEvent>
        <eventName>Begin of process - ${camelId}</eventName>
        <eventType>START</eventType>
        <eventDescription>Replication process started</eventDescription>
        <eventAttributes>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>BTP-IS MessageId</name>
                <value>${header.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Cobrainer Job Architecture Id</name>
                <value>${property.cbrJobArchitecture}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Cobrainer SFSF Family Context</name>
                <value>${property.sfsfFamilyContext}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>TOTAL Cobrainer Job Families SELECTED</name>
                <value>${property.sumJobFamily}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Families TO BE CREATED</name>
                <value>${property.sumCreate}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Total SFSF Job Families TO BE RESYNCHED</name>
                <value>${property.sumUpdate}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
        </eventAttributes>
    </EMEvent>
</EMEvent>
